sters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwic9oq5t-uTAxX9fcIBHdP1FDJIk9HElbmk0KZ8ygEEPtW6hw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbnBRa1NOdGNyQzg1UXNfc2VxTnN0S1RQeXFXZ3xBQ3Jtc0trVkZ1ZWVlYlNxOWJUdXJKS05uT3dVVERVcVFLTmpWb1pkSTFRSk15VTNuSDdlQnFKRGN2cnlUdElvZDRyYXBpSmtoVkh2M0pIWU5EMVA5eHRtbndiYnlWellURnFnX0phZ3dXbGhaaTRMYWpkMllWWQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=fE1BI5KxKJM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbnBRa1NOdGNyQzg1UXNfc2VxTnN0S1RQeXFXZ3xBQ3Jtc0trVkZ1ZWVlYlNxOWJUdXJKS05uT3dVVERVcVFLTmpWb1pkSTFRSk15VTNuSDdlQnFKRGN2cnlUdElvZDRyYXBpSmtoVkh2M0pIWU5EMVA5eHRtbndiYnlWellURnFnX0phZ3dXbGhaaTRMYWpkMllWWQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=fE1BI5KxKJM","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwic9oq5t-uTAxX9fcIBHdP1FDJIk9HElbmk0KZ8ygEEPtW6hw==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa25aSGVOSFVLVjhqOW9UejRKVndjaE9OUzA0UXxBQ3Jtc0trUU1TTWozRU1jbnQ3VXF2dnJxMHRXN3RKLU9KUldldWF1UXdHdTJpUkRCbDdzRnhueE50cGtFZUpNVzJBQXhYV2UtWkcxS3RpZjNIYVVHZkJ0OGx2N0tWREEtV3NzX3BxSng3UkJzYkUtQmhiV2tQZw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2